title: Episode #47 - Matt Fulchiron, Brandon Wardell, & ME
description: Recorded on the Road in my hotel in DC... Matt "The Full Charge" Fulchiron & I sit down with young comic Brandon Wardell and talk comedy, awkwardness, and skateboarding.
